我喜欢阅读；她喜欢跳舞。

list.abstract: Dancing意为舞蹈，是暴雪公司出品的游戏《魔兽争霸3：混乱之治》（包括他的资料片《魔兽争霸3：冰封王座》）微操作名称。它是一个在星际时代就流行的短语，意思是把受伤的单位拉回来再用快捷键SHIFT+A打回去，这样可以短暂的转移对方的火力。

yingyinNormal.en: Grace and beauty. Peppa loves dancing. Everyone loves dancing.
yingyinNormal.zh: 动作要做得优雅美丽。佩琪喜欢跳舞，大家都喜欢跳舞。

yingyinNormal.en: Moondance? Yeah, he's, not dancing anymore.
yingyinNormal.zh: 小月舞吗？是的，他已经没法跳舞了。

yingyinNormal.en: Don't you have to pee? That's why I'm dancing.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你不想尿了？这就是我跳舞的原因。

yingyinNormal.en: We've been dancing to Granny and Grandpa's favorite record.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们在听爷爷奶奶最喜欢的唱片跳舞呢！

yingyinNormal.en: Dancing is my life.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我的人生就是跳舞。

yingyinNormal.en: Suzy Sheep, what is your talent? Dancing No. you can't dance.
yingyinNormal.zh: 小羊苏西，你的才艺是什么呢？跳舞。不行，你不能跳舞。

yingyinNormal.en: I was going to do skipping. But I can still do dancing and singing. My talent is singing. Twinkle, twinkle, little star. I can still do dancing.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我也准备要表演跳绳的。不过我还可以表演跳舞和唱歌呢。我的才艺是唱歌。一闪一闪亮晶晶。没关系，我还可以表演跳舞。

yingyinNormal.en: I know Bouboo. We've been dancing against each other since a while.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我知道布布，我们比赛跳舞很久了。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh, we are so taking you dancing. No, you most certainly are not.
yingyinNormal.zh: 哦，我们一定一定要带你跳舞去。不，你们更多的肯定是不想带。

yingyinNormal.en: Mummy. Hello. We've been dancing to Granny and Grandpa's favorite record. Yes.
yingyinNormal.zh: 妈妈！你们好啊！我们在听爷爷奶奶最喜欢的唱片跳舞呢！是的。

yingyinNormal.en: It is evening. Peppa and George are in the sitting room dancing to their favourite song.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在是晚上。佩奇和乔治在客厅里听着他们最喜欢的音乐跳舞。

yingyinNormal.en: It is evening. Peppa and George are in the sitting room dancing to their favourite song.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在是晚上。佩奇和乔治在客厅里听着他们最喜欢的音乐跳舞。

yingyinNormal.en: It is evening. Peppa and George are in the sitting room dancing to their favourite song.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在是晚上。佩佩和乔治正在客厅里随着他们最喜欢的歌跳舞。

yingyinNormal.en: What's the difference? Dancing cats and a new planet are just gonna get replaced by something new tomorrow.
yingyinNormal.zh: 有什么关系呢？跳舞猫和新行星明天就会被新东西替代。

yingyinNormal.en: Are you a dancing reindeer? No, Sergeant. Are you contradicting me, Private? No, Sargeant. Good.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你是跳舞的驯鹿？不，中士。你在反驳我，列兵？不，中士。好。

yingyinNormal.en: The Bay City Rollers for dancing. Wait, that was from my sixth grade wedding.
yingyinNormal.zh: 三重奏跳舞时用湾市摇滚（七八十年代的合唱团），等一下，那是我的六年级婚礼。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, don't judge me. So, what do you want to do, go to the movies, go dancing, lay down for a little bit?
yingyinNormal.zh: 好吧，别怪我，你们想玩什么？看电影，去跳舞，还是去躺一会？

yingyinNormal.en: It is Talent Day. My talents are skipping, singing and dancing. I practiced them all last night.
yingyinNormal.zh: 今天是才艺日。我的才艺是跳绳，唱歌，还有跳舞。我昨天晚上都已经练习过了。

yingyinNormal.en: You know, walking to school together, dancing on tables at bungalow, night swimming at your mom's country house.
yingyinNormal.zh: 一起上学，一起在平房里的桌上跳舞，晚上在你妈妈乡村别墅的泳池里游泳。

yingyinNormal.en: Dancing? Yeah, I don't know, Penny... The thing is, we're not... No, we're really more of a... No.
yingyinNormal.zh: 跳舞？嗯，我不能确定，佩妮...其实，我们不太... 我们更适合... 不行。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2018-2021年全国重点省市中考试卷，包括听力、阅读、完形、单选、填空、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: Which club do you prefer to join, the chess club or the <highlight>dancing</highlight> club?
examination_example.sentence_trans: 你更喜欢加入哪个俱乐部，象棋俱乐部还是舞蹈俱乐部？

examination_example.sentence: She is going to have a <highlight>dancing</highlight> class.
Traditional Chinese drama, including Beijing Opera, is a kind of entertainment which includes spoken parts, singing, <highlight>dancing</highlight> and acrobatics.
